":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"95% 真係去到好盡 開8成比D湯人飲下都好丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c195a02bc90f1178d8ce48c911d636271858d96d","tid":2085111,"uid":17245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"根本個回佣制度令到個市場唔透明"},{"pid":"f93c3a4780754b12f0afb302a3403a83cf422dab","tid":2085111,"uid":51134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"諗起早2日有個置業post...<br />\n成埋agent入嚟<br />\n個個都話: 回8成5/9成/9成半 tg我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49074cd287eba9a9e596cbf9962cd7d183185ba","tid":2085111,"uid":295931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:10:26.000Z","msg":"温故知新<br />\n<br />\n問：新盤回佣是否違法？<br />\n<br />\n答：地產代理監管局就新盤佣金回贈一事向地產代理發出有關發放佣金回贈的指引，因此客戶向代理要求提供新盤回贈佣金並不會觸犯法例。"},{"pid":"e38ab6b7e904096e1f007db2d1c5e1a503ac5230","tid":2085111,"uid":30274,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"我以為8成半已經好過份<br />\n原來可以去到9成半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班aa狗要餓狗搶屎了<br />\n<br />\n不過講番轉頭，如果唔回佣，條aa狗可以有37萬袋，on99，唔怪得成日話做地產好搵。做啲手辦眼見功夫就有30幾萬袋，食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"cc701a49e600a7366ca8ef6481763e1f2554a018","tid":2085111,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"唔係入票落訂先有得抽咩<br />\n抽中左都無金錢損失？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3308d5f58259ecdbfca378e4ba41312a0b2a50","tid":2085111,"uid":72228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e38ab6b7e904096e1f007db2d1c5e1a503ac5230","tid":2085111,"uid":30274,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"我以為8成半已經好過份<br />\n原來可以去到9成半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班aa狗要餓狗搶屎了<br />\n<br />\n不過講番轉頭，如果唔回佣，條aa狗可以有37萬袋，on99，唔怪得成日話做地產好搵。做啲手辦眼見功夫就有30幾萬袋，食撚屎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"地產狗易開單就唔洗回佣回到9成半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇死佢地盡地一鋪以為個買家會死頂照搵佢地買"},{"pid":"0db54a032e4318e3a9761c11df1b4291162d66e2","tid":2085111,"uid":163881,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"2手就話啫，1手樓aa作用除咗回佣仲可以做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過回95% 9成9隻aa狗寫錯terms"},{"pid":"d35f997ed48192d1b811d92607e358dc67641bdf","tid":2085111,"uid":89225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cf4dd0fba760014d66597644b27a9299952b895b","tid":2085111,"uid":85190,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"所以話AA點解咁黑人憎 成日諗埋d屎橋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"AA後面一定要加個狗字就係咁解"}]}